      <title>GitHub Hexo报错汇总</title>
      <link href="/2020/06/03/github-hexo-bao-cuo-hui-zong/"/>
      <url>/2020/06/03/github-hexo-bao-cuo-hui-zong/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ol><li><p><code>$ hexo init</code></p><p> 网络问题初始化失败，删除所有hexo安装包以后重新输入<code>$ npm intall -g hexo-cli</code>失败</p><p> 尝试<code>$ npm intall -g --foece hexo-cli</code>成功, <code>--force</code> 可以暴力覆盖</p><p> 其实<code>$ hexo init</code>不需要重装hexo-cli服务</p></li></ol><a id="more"></a><ol start="2"><li><p><code>npm set registry[http://registry.npmjs.org/](http://registry.npmjs.org/)</code></p><p> 可以重置链接</p></li><li><p><a href="https://www.notion.so/7b7de4fac9224d1e9e95cec6e64855c3" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.notion.so/7b7de4fac9224d1e9e95cec6e64855c3</a></p></li><li><p>Hi, sorry, i must hv done something wrong.<br>i tried to point, which i hv just bought from you, to But now when i type, the browser shows a</p><p>结果应该是Domain提供商反应比较慢，现在好了</p></li><li><p>hexo deploy not found git<br>是因为没有装<code>$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</code></p></li><li><p>优化过程中出现TypeError Cannot read property ‘replace’ of null<br>实在是悲剧，找不到原因，只好$ hexo init 从头来过，哭哭<br>切记每步操作完一定要$ hexo g&amp;d</p></li><li><p>FATAL Cannot read property ‘replace’ of null<br>是因为config文件里的url: 后面被删掉了</p></li><li><p>hexo-更改本地路径<br>a. config.yml文件中配置如下：<br>b. hexo s -p 5000</p></li></ol><ol start="9"><li>未完待续</li></ol><script>        document.querySelectorAll('.github-emoji')          .forEach(el => {            if (!el.dataset.src) { return; }            const img = document.createElement('img');            img.style = 'display:none !important;';            img.src = el.dataset.src;            img.addEventListener('error', () => {              img.remove();              el.style.color = 'inherit';              el.style.backgroundImage = 'none';              el.style.background = 'none';            });            img.addEventListener('load', () => {              img.remove();            });            document.body.appendChild(img);          });      </script>]]></content>
      
      
      
